# A Terraform configuration typically contains:
# Mot cau hinh Terraform thong thuong chua:
#
# 1. Provider blocks - specify which cloud/service provider to use
# 2. Resource blocks - define infrastructure components
# 3. Variable blocks - parameterize configurations
# 4. Output blocks - display information after apply
#
# 1. Provider blocks - chi dinh nha cung cap dam may/dich vu nao de su dung
# 2. Resource blocks - dinh nghia cac thanh phan ha tang
# 3. Variable blocks - tham so hoa cau hinh
# 4. Output blocks - hien thi thong tin sau khi ap dung

